rComments: Jason is amazing. Hands down one of the best prof's I've had. I almost cried when I found out that he was leaving U of T. He pushes you to your limits, and doesn't let you half ass anything. Talk to him outside of class! He's willing to help you out, and really appreciates students who are actively participating. TAKE HIS CLASS!!!

Truly amazing professor, had him last year for HIS106 and it was a real honour being in this class. He's clear, concise, friendly, and very detailed in his lectures. Makes them engaging and easy to follow. I learned a lot in his class, lecture attendance is important! Super approachable and always talked to students.
